---
import Layout from "../layouts/Default.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy" showBackLink={true}>
  <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">Status of This Memo</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This document specifies the privacy practices for all services, websites, and applications 
          provided by me, unless explicitly stated otherwise on such service, website, or application.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This is a privacy policy. It's supposed to tell you what data I collect about you.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The short version: I don't collect any data about you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">2. Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          I don't use analytics. I don't use tracking cookies. I don't collect personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">3. What This Means</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          You can browse these sites without worrying about being tracked or having your data sold. 
          Because there's no data to track or sell.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">4. Changes</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If this ever changes, I'll update this page. But I don't plan on collecting data anytime soon.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-[#888888]">5. Questions</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have questions about this policy, you can reach me through the contact information 
          on my website.
        </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
